cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image generation and analysis. The use of deep generative models also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The statistical analysis of the generated images could also place it in the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the analysis of image components and filters could suggest a potential fit with the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
